<body>
	
<header>
<div id="instruction">
When asked about your studies or work, you will need to use certain tenses to describe your activities. Match the tenses a candidate should use to the situations.
</div>
</header>
	
<section id="noscroll">
  <span id="a7" draggable="true">past continuous</span>
  <span id="a8" draggable="true">present continuous</span>
  <span id="a9" draggable="true">present perfect continuous</span>
  <span id="a12" draggable="true">present simple</span>
  <span id="a6" draggable="true">past simple</span>
  <span id="a11" draggable="true">future (with 'will' or 'going to')</span>
  <span id="a10" draggable="true">present perfect</span>
</section>

<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/set4_03.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  
  <ol id="questionList">
  <li>3 years ago - Finish school<tab/><tab/><tab/><input id="q1" type="droptarget"/></li>
  <li>Over the last year - Prepare for final exams<tab/><input id="q2" type="droptarget"/></li>
  <li>Now - Not yet done exams<tab/><tab/><tab/><input id="q3" type="droptarget"/></li>
  <li>Next year - Do further studies<tab/><tab/><tab/><input id="q4" type="droptarget"/></li>
  <li>Most days - Work hard<tab/><tab/><tab/><tab/><input id="q5" type="droptarget"/></li>
  </ol>
</section>

<section id="fb1">
  <p class="feedbacktext">1. This is not in the present.<br/>
  You don't need to use continuous here. The word&#xA0;<b>ago</b>&#xA0;does not refer to the future.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb2">
  <p class="feedbacktext">2. This is not a habit or something you always do.<br/>
  There is a period of time involved that is not over yet. The word&#xA0;<b>last</b>&#xA0;is not used for the future.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb3">
  <p class="popuptext1">3. This is not something that happened in the past.<br/>
  And it is not happening now.</p>
  <p class="popuptext2"><b>Yet</b>&#xA0;means 'until now', so we are not talking about the future.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb4">
  <p class="feedbacktext">4.&#xA0;<b>Next year</b>&#xA0;is not in the past or the present.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb5">
  <p class="feedbacktext">5. This is a habit, not a current action. We are interested in now.</p>
</section>

